<div><head>會稽典錄</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.2">夏方，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.3">字文公，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.4">家遭疫癘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.5">父母伯叔一時死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.6">凡十三喪。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.7">方年十四，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.8">晝則負土哀號，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.9">暮則扶棺哭泣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.10">比葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.11">年十七，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.12">烏鳥聚集，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-1a.13">猛獸乳其側。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.2">夏香，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.3">字曼卿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.4">永興人也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.5">年十五，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.6">縣長葛君會客飲宴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.7">時郡遭大旱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.8">香進諫曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.9">「昔殷湯遭旱，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.10">以六事自責，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.11">而雨澤應澍。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.12">成王悔過，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.13">偃禾復起。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.14">自古先聖畏懼天異，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.15">必思變復，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.16">以濟民命。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.17">今始罹天災，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.18">縣界獨甚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.19">未聞明達崇殷周之德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.20">飲宴獨歡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.21">百姓枯瘁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.22">神祇有靈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.23">必不享也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.24">百姓不足，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.25">君孰與足？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.26">宜當還守。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.27">即罷會，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.28">身損俸祿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1322_CHANT_001-2a.29">以贍民飢。<lb/></seg>
</p>
